original_title: The Guitar Artistry of John Fahey - On the Sunny Side of the Ocean
overview: Titles include: "Red Pony, Death of the Clayton Peacock, In Christ There Is No East or West, Poor Boy. Medley: "Twilight On Prince George's Avenue and O Holy Night and My Prayer", Who Will Rock The Cradle, Steamboat 'Gwine Round The Bend, The Story of Dorothy Gooch, Part One, Guitar Rag, On The Sunnyside Side Of The Ocean, Medley: "Blueberry and Special Rider", St. Vitus Dance, Dorothy, City of Refuge, Mexico, and Discarded".
title: The Guitar Artistry of John Fahey - On the Sunny Side of the Ocean
